柱状图¶

In [12]:
def cal_lis(name):
    temp = data_1[data_1['NAME'] == name]
    avl_income_country = [float(round(each /1000,2)) for each in temp['农村家庭可支配（元）'].tolist()]
    avl_income_city = [float(round(each /1000,2)) for each in temp['城市家庭可支配（元）'].tolist()]
    incomes_city = [float(round(each /1000,2)) for each in temp['城镇总收入（元）'].tolist()]
    incomes_country = [float(round(each /1000,2)) for each in temp['农村总收入（元）'].tolist()]
    return avl_income_country,avl_income_city,incomes_country,incomes_city
In [13]:
def plot_line(timeData,avl_income,incomes,title,s1,s2):
    bar1 = (
        Bar()
        .add_xaxis(timeData)
        .add_yaxis(series_name=s1,y_axis=incomes)
        .extend_axis(
            yaxis=opts.AxisOpts(
                axislabel_opts=opts.LabelOpts(formatter="{value}"), interval=5
            )
        )
        .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
                        itemstyle_opts=opts.ItemStyleOpts(opacity=0.8))
        .set_global_opts(
            tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(is_show=False),
            xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(
                axislabel_opts={"interval":"0"}
              ),  
            yaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(axislabel_opts=opts.LabelOpts(formatter="{value}")),
        )
    )

    line1 = Line().add_xaxis(timeData).add_yaxis(
                            series_name=s2,
                            y_axis=avl_income,
                            symbol_size=8,
                            is_hover_animation=False,
                            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
                            linestyle_opts=opts.LineStyleOpts(width=1.5),
                            is_smooth=True,
                            yaxis_index=1
                        ).set_global_opts(
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(
                title=title, subtitle="2000年-2019年", pos_left="center"
            ),
            tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(trigger="axis"),
            axispointer_opts=opts.AxisPointerOpts(
                is_show=True, link=[{"xAxisIndex": "all"}]
            ),
            datazoom_opts=[
                opts.DataZoomOpts(
                    is_show=True,
                    is_realtime=True,
                    start_value=30,
                    end_value=70,
                    xaxis_index=[0, 1],
                )
            ],
            xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(
                type_="category",
                boundary_gap=False,
                axisline_opts=opts.AxisLineOpts(is_on_zero=True),
            ),
            yaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(name="元"),
            legend_opts=opts.LegendOpts(pos_left="left"),
            toolbox_opts=opts.ToolboxOpts(
                is_show=True,
                feature={
                    "dataZoom": {"yAxisIndex": "none"},
                    "restore": {},
                    "saveAsImage": {},
                },
            ),
        )
    bar1.overlap(line1)
    return bar1
In [14]:
avl_income_country,avl_income_city,incomes_country,incomes_city = cal_lis(names[0])
chart1 = plot_line(years,avl_income_country,incomes_country,names[0]+'农村收入变化一览表','农村总收入','农村家庭可支配收入')
chart2 = plot_line(years,avl_income_city,incomes_city,names[0]+'城市收入变化一览表','城市总收入','城市家庭可支配收入')
tab1 = Tab()
tab1.add(chart1, names[0]+'农村收入变化一览表')
tab1.add(chart2, names[0]+'城市收入变化一览表')
tab1.render_notebook()

折线图¶

In [17]:
def cal_lis1(name):
    temp = data_1[data_1['NAME'] == name]
    rate = [float(round(each,2)) for each in temp['城镇化率'].tolist()]
    population = [float(round(each,2)) for each in temp['城镇总人口（万人）'].tolist()]
    max_num = temp['城镇总人口（万人）'].max()
    return rate,population,max_num
In [18]:
def plot_mul_line(s1,s2,title,timeData,rate1,rate2,rate3,population1,population2,population3,max_num):
    l1 = (
        Line()
        .add_xaxis(xaxis_data=timeData)
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name=s1[0],
            y_axis=population1,
            symbol_size=8,
            is_hover_animation=False,
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
            linestyle_opts=opts.LineStyleOpts(width=1.5),
            is_smooth=True,
        )
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name=s1[1],
            y_axis=population2,
            symbol_size=8,
            is_hover_animation=False,

柱状图¶

In [20]:
def format_data(data: dict) -> dict:
    for year in range(2000, 2020):
        max_data, sum_data = 0, 0
        temp = data[year]
        max_data = max(temp)
        for i in range(len(temp)):
            sum_data += temp[i]
            data[year][i] = {"name": names[i], "value": temp[i]}
        data[str(year) + "max"] = int(max_data / 100) * 100
        data[str(year) + "sum"] = sum_data
    return data

# 统一地图地区名称
name_list = []
for each in names:
    temp_lis = each.split(' ')
    pro = ''
    for each1 in temp_lis:
        pro += each1
    if pro == '上海':
        pro = '上海市'
    elif pro == '重庆':
        pro = '重庆市'
    elif pro == '天津':
        pro ='天津市'
    elif pro == '内蒙古':
        pro ='内蒙古自治区'
    elif pro == '新疆':
        pro = '新疆维吾尔自治区'
    elif pro == '广西':
        pro = '广西壮族自治区'
    elif pro == '西藏':
        pro = '西藏自治区'
    else:
        pro = pro + '省'
    name_list.append(pro)

def format_data(data: dict) -> dict:
    for year in range(2000, 2020):
        max_data, sum_data = 0, 0
        temp = data[year]
        max_data = max(temp)
        for i in range(len(temp)):
            sum_data += temp[i]
            data[year][i] = (name_list[i],temp[i])
        data[str(year) + "max"] = int(max_data / 100) * 100
        data[str(year) + "sum"] = sum_data
    return data

                is_show=True, trigger="axis", axis_pointer_type="shadow"
            ),
            legend_opts=opts.LegendOpts(is_show=False,pos_left="40%"),
    ))
    return c

In [35]:
def get_year_overlap_chart(year: int) -> Bar:
    bar = (
        Bar()
        .add_xaxis(xaxis_data=names)
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name="居民可支配收入",
            y_axis=total_data["dataINCOME"][year],
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name="城市可支配收入",
            y_axis=total_data["dataCITY"][year],
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name="农村可支配收入",
            y_axis=total_data["dataCOUNTRY"][year],
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        .set_global_opts(
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(
                title="{}全国可支配收入情况一览".format(year), subtitle="2000年-2019年"
            ),
            tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(
                is_show=True, trigger="axis", axis_pointer_type="shadow"
            ),
            xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(axislabel_opts={"interval":"0","rotate":45}),
            legend_opts=opts.LegendOpts(pos_left="40%"),
    ))
    pie = (
        Pie()
        .add(
            series_name="可支配收入占比",
            data_pair=[
                ["城市", total_data["dataCITY"]["{}sum".format(year)]],
                ["农村", total_data["dataCOUNTRY"]["{}sum".format(year)]],
            ],
            center=["75%", "35%"],
            radius="28%",
        )
        .set_series_opts(tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(is_show=True, trigger="item"))
    )
    return bar.overlap(pie)

# 生成时间轴的图
timeline3 = Timeline()

for y in range(2000, 2020):
    timeline3.add(get_year_overlap_chart(year=y), time_point=str(y))

def get_year_overlap_chart(year: int) -> Bar:
    bar = (
        Bar()
        .add_xaxis(xaxis_data=names)
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name="总人口",
            y_axis=total_data["dataPOP"][year],
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name="城镇人口",
            y_axis=total_data["dataCITY"][year],
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        .add_yaxis(
            series_name="农村人口",
            y_axis=total_data["dataCOUNTRY"][year],
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        .set_global_opts(
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(
                title="{}全国人口组成".format(year), subtitle="2000年-2019年"
            ),
            tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(
                is_show=True, trigger="axis", axis_pointer_type="shadow"
            ),
            xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(axislabel_opts={"interval":"0","rotate":45}),
        )
    )
    pie = (
        Pie()
        .add(
            series_name="人口组成",
            data_pair=[
                ["城镇", total_data["dataCITY"]["{}sum".format(year)]],
                ["农村", total_data["dataCOUNTRY"]["{}sum".format(year)]],
            ],
            center=["85%", "35%"],
            radius="28%",
        )
        .set_series_opts(tooltip_opts=opts.TooltipOpts(is_show=True, trigger="item"))
    )
    return bar.overlap(pie)

全国各地区人均收入、消费支出排行榜¶

In [42]:
from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Bar

# 准备数据
regions = data_2['地区']
income = data_2['人均可支配收入']
expenditure = data_2['消费支出']

# 创建Bar实例
bar_chart = (
    Bar()
    .add_xaxis(list(regions))
    .add_yaxis("人均可支配收入", list(income))
    .add_yaxis("消费支出", list(expenditure))
    .reversal_axis()
    .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(position="right"))
    .set_global_opts(
        title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="全国各地区人均收入、消费支出排行榜"),
        xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(name="金额（元）"),
        yaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(name="地区",axislabel_opts={"interval":"0"},min_=-1,max_=32),
    )
)


bar_chart.render_notebook()
Out[42]:

全国及各地区消费占比¶

In [43]:
from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Bar

stack_bar = (
#     Bar(init_opts=opts.InitOpts(width="900px", height="500px"))
    Bar()
    .add_xaxis(data_2["地区"].tolist())
    .add_yaxis("总消费支出占比", data_2["消费支出占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("食品烟酒占比", data_2["食品烟酒占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("衣着占比", data_2["衣着占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("居住占比", data_2["居住占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("生活用品及服务占比", data_2["生活用品及服务占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("交通通信占比", data_2["交通通信占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("教育文化娱乐占比", data_2["教育文化娱乐占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("医疗保健占比", data_2["医疗保健占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    .add_yaxis("其他用品及服务占比", data_2["其他用品及服务占比"].tolist(), stack="stack1")
    # 在系列设置中设置标签属性
    .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title='全国及各地区消费占比',
                                               pos_left='45%'
                                               ),
                     legend_opts=opts.LegendOpts(
                         #可滚动翻页的图例。当图例数量较多时可以使用。
#                          type_='scroll',
                         #图例的位置
                         pos_left='right',
                         pos_top='middle',
                         orient='vertical'#horizontal #图例方式的方式
                        ),
                     xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(axislabel_opts={"interval":"0","rotate":45}),
                    )
        .set_series_opts(
#             label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(position="inside", color="white", font_size=15)
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(
                #不显示数据标签
                is_show=False
            )
        )
)

stack_bar.render_notebook()

from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Bar, Line,Page
# from pyecharts.globals import ThemeType
# # 全局设置主题颜色
# theme_config = ThemeType.CHALK  # 颜色方案

# 创建一个Page对象，并将图表添加到页面中
page = Page(layout=Page.DraggablePageLayout)
page.add(table)
# page.add(tab)
page.add(line_data)
page.add(timeline1)
page.add(timeline2)
page.add(timeline3)
page.add(timeline4)
page.add(bar_chart)
page.add(stack_bar)

# 生成HTML文件并在浏览器中打开并修改
page.render("临时可视化大屏.html")
